      • EPContextObject

        public EPContextObject(java.lang.String key,
                       java.lang.Object value,
                       java.lang.String formattedValue,
                       java.lang.String base64)

        An EPContextObject represents a valu stored into a chat conversation context.

        Parameters:
        key - The context key
        value - The value associated with the context key. This is the raw value. For example, for a date it will be the timestamp.
        formattedValue - The formatted value to display in a message instead of the value itself.
        base64 - A data base 64 string if this context object represents a file.
